{"cursor":"9805","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"{{Infobox law firm\n| name = Borden Ladner Gervais LLP logo = num_attorneys = 750+ num_offices = 6\n| practice_areas = General practice headquarters = Ottawa, Toronto, Montreal,\n| Calgary, Vancouver, Waterloo Region date_founded = 2000 firm_location =\n| Ottawa, Toronto, Montreal, Calgary, Vancouver, Waterloo Region industry = Law\n| Firm homepage = [http://www.blg.com blg.com]|\n}}\n\n'Borden Ladner Gervais LLP' (abbreviated as 'BLG') is the largest full-service\nCanadian law firm. The firm has over 750 lawyers, intellectual property agents\nand other professionals in offices in Calgary, MontrÃ©al, Ottawa, Toronto,\nVancouver and Waterloo Region. [http://www.blg.com/home/blg-home BLG\nWebsite]  BLG does not designate one of its offices as its headquarters,\nbut instead is governed by a national council composed of partners from across\nCanada. Sean Weir [http://www.blg.com/en/home/our-professionals/Pages/Weir-\nSean.aspx Sean Weir Biography] has been National Managing Partner of the\nfirm since 2000.\n\nIn 2011 â for the fifth consecutive year â BLG was recognized as a âGo-To Law\nFirmâ for Fortune 500\ncompanies. http://pdfserver.amlaw.com/nlj/2010_Fortune_Section_6_FINAL.pdf\n The firm was also ranked number one in Canada for the number of lawyers\n(190) it had recognized in the 2012 edition of The Best Lawyers in Canada\n[http://www.bestlawyers.com/search/firmProfile.aspx?firm_ID=38017 Best\nLawyers in Canada]  and had the most number of lawyers in Canada with a\nMartindale-Hubbell Peer Review Rating. [http://www.martindale.com/Borden-Ladner-Gervais-LLP/law-firm-\n1081999-peer-review-ratings.htm Martindale-Hubbell] \n\nThe firm also supports a variety of activities by providing pro bono legal\nservices, fundraising and volunteer programs. In 2010, BLG was recognized by the\n2010 Canadian Pro Bono Awards with the Canadian National Law Firm Award for\ncontribution to the delivery of pro bono legal services across the country. [http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/2010-Canadian-Pro-Bono-\nAwards-Highlight-the-Power-of-Pro-Bono-1306026.htm \"2010 Canadian Pro Bono\nAwards Highlight the Power of Pro Bono\" - Pro Bono Law Alberta] \n","linknr":192,"url":"Borden_Ladner_Gervais","recorded":1374767319,"links":["/w/index.php?title=Borden_Ladner_Gervais&action=edit","/w/index.php?title=Borden_Ladner_Gervais&action=edit","//bits.wikimedia.org/favicon/wikipedia.ico","/w/opensearch_desc.php","//en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=rsd","//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/","/w/index.php?title=Special:RecentChanges&feed=atom","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=ext.gadget.DRN-wizard%2CReferenceTooltips%2Ccharinsert%2Cteahouse%7Cext.rtlcite%2Cwikihiero%7Cext.uls.nojs%7Cmediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmw.PopUpMediaTransform%7Cskins.vector&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=site&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=startup&only=scripts&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/geoiplookup","//meta.wikimedia.org","#mw-navigation","#p-search","/wiki/File:BLG_Logo-En_SM.jpg","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/43/BLG_Logo-En_SM.jpg","/wiki/Ottawa","/wiki/Toronto","/wiki/Montreal","/wiki/Calgary","/wiki/Vancouver","/wiki/Waterloo_Region","http://www.blg.com","/wiki/Law_firm","#cite_note-1","#cite_note-2","#cite_note-3","#cite_note-4","/wiki/Martindale-Hubbell","#cite_note-5","#cite_note-6","#History","#Founding_Firms","#Notable_alumni","#References","#External_links","/w/index.php?title=Borden_Ladner_Gervais&action=edit&section=1","#cite_note-7","#cite_note-autogenerated1-8","#cite_note-9","#cite_note-10","#cite_note-11","/w/index.php?title=Borden_Ladner_Gervais&action=edit&section=2","#cite_note-autogenerated1-8","#cite_note-12","#cite_note-autogenerated1-8","#cite_note-13","#cite_note